17 B. For purposes of this section, creditable service shall
18 include service credit reciprocally recognized pursuant to Section
19 901 et seq. of this title but for eligibility purposes only.
20 C. The duration of participation in the Oklahoma Public
21 Employees Deferred Option Plan for a member shall not exceed five
22 (5) years. Participation in the Oklahoma Public Employees Deferred
23 Option Plan must begin the first day of a month and end on the last
24 day of a month. At the conclusion of a member's participation in
